#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "The User Interface"
msgstr "Uporabniški vmesnik"

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kxstitch; Main Window"
msgstr "&kxstitch; Glavno okno"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: ui.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screen shot of &kxstitch;"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kxstitch;"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kxstitch; main window consists of an editor window shown on the right "
"in the image above with three dock windows. The dock windows provide a "
"preview of the pattern, the palette of flosses and a history list. If an "
"image is imported, an additional dock window showing a preview of the "
"original image for reference will be shown. Each of these dock windows can "
"be moved around to various edges of the main window, detached from the view "
"or turned off and back on."
msgstr ""
"&kxstitch; glavno okno je sestavljeno iz okna urejevalnika, prikazanega na "
"desni na zgornji sliki, s tremi priklopnimi okni. Priključna okna nudijo "
"predogled vzorca, palete nitkanj in seznam zgodovine. Če je slika uvožena, "
"bo prikazano dodatno priklopno okno, ki prikazuje predogled izvirne slike za "
"referenco. Vsako od teh priklopnih oken lahko premaknete na različne robove "
"glavnega okna, jih ločite od pogleda ali izklopite in znova vklopite."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The sections are divided by splitters, which can be moved to change the "
"amount of space allocated to any of the sections."
msgstr ""
"Odseki so razdeljeni z razdelilniki, ki jih lahko premikate, da spremenite "
"količino prostora, dodeljenega kateremu koli razdelku."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The layout of other elements, menu bar, toolbars and the status bar, is "
"similar to other &kde; applications you run."
msgstr ""
"Postavitev drugih elementov, menijske vrstice, orodnih vrstic in statusne "
"vrstice, je podobna drugim &kde; aplikacijam, ki jih izvajate."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The status bar at the bottom of the window shows various status messages."
msgstr "Vrstica stanja na dnu okna prikazuje različna sporočila o stanju."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor Window"
msgstr "Okno urejevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main editing window shows a grid pattern and scales top and left. The "
"scales can be formatted in stitches, centimeters or inches. The editor is a "
"scrolling, zoomable view of your pattern and allows you to use the various "
"editing tools to modify your design."
msgstr ""
"Glavno okno za urejanje prikazuje vzorec mreže in lestvice zgoraj in levo. "
"Lestvice je mogoče formatirati v šivih, centimetrih ali palcih. Urejevalnik "
"je pomični pogled vašega vzorca z možnostjo povečave in vam omogoča uporabo "
"različnih orodij za urejanje za spreminjanje vašega dizajna."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Generally the &LMB; is used to activate any of the tools on the pattern. "
"Details of each of the tools and their use is shown in <link linkend="
"\"commands\">the command reference section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Na splošno &LMB; se uporablja za aktiviranje katerega koli orodja na vzorcu. "
"Podrobnosti o vsakem orodju in njihovi uporabi so prikazane v <link linkend="
"\"commands\">razdelku z referenčnimi informacijami o ukazih</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The grid shows heavier lines dividing the cells into groups. The number of "
"cells per group is configurable, the default is 10, as are the colors for "
"the lines. This is useful if you are creating patterns on a dark colored "
"canvas that requires lighter colored lines for contrast."
msgstr ""
"Mreža prikazuje debelejše črte, ki delijo celice v skupine. Število celic na "
"skupino je nastavljivo, privzeto je 10, prav tako barve za črte. To je "
"uporabno, če ustvarjate vzorce na temnem platnu, ki za kontrast zahteva "
"svetlejše črte."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A menu option allows you to add background images to the editor window, to "
"use as a template for adding stitches. For more details see the section on "
"<link linkend=\"creatingpatterns\">Creating Patterns</link>."
msgstr ""
"Možnost menija vam omogoča, da v okno urejevalnika dodate slike ozadja, ki "
"jih uporabite kot predlogo za dodajanje šivov. Za več podrobnosti si oglejte "
"razdelek <link linkend=\"creatingpatterns\">Ustvarjanje vzorcev</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:54 ui.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context Menu"
msgstr "Kontekstni meni"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using your &RMB; on the editor will activate a context menu allowing you to "
"change the format of the scales and the visual appearance of the stitches. "
"It also allows you to toggle on or off the background images, the stitches, "
"backstitches, the grid and the scales."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo &RMB; v urejevalniku aktivira kontekstni meni, ki vam omogoča "
"spreminjanje formata lestvic in vizualnega videza šivov. Omogoča tudi vklop "
"ali izklop slik ozadja, šivov, hrbtnih šivov, mreže in lestvic."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview Window"
msgstr "Okno za predogled"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> window shows a scrolling overview of the "
"current design at a smaller scale than the Editor window. The "
"<guilabel>Preview</guilabel> shows a black rectangle representing the "
"current view within the Editor window."
msgstr ""
"Okno <guilabel>Predogled</guilabel> prikazuje drsni pregled trenutnega "
"dizajna v manjšem obsegu kot okno urejevalnika. <guilabel>Predogled</"
"guilabel> prikazuje črn pravokotnik, ki predstavlja trenutni pogled v oknu "
"urejevalnika."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By clicking the &LMB; within the preview window, the Editor window will be "
"centered on that point. Additionally by pressing down the &LMB; and dragging "
"a rectangle around an area, the Editor window will be zoomed to encompass "
"that area."
msgstr ""
"S klikom &LMB; v oknu za predogled bo okno urejevalnika osredotočeno na to "
"točko. Poleg tega s pritiskom &LMB; in povlečete pravokotnik okoli območja, "
"bo okno urejevalnika povečano, da zajame to območje."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Palette Window"
msgstr "Okno Paleta"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Palette</guilabel> window shows the floss colors currently in "
"this patterns palette as colored blocks, and optionally with the symbols "
"that are associated with each color. Moving the mouse pointer over a color "
"block will pop up a tool tip showing the color number and name for that "
"color. Clicking on a color selects that color for the next painting or "
"drawing function."
msgstr ""
"Okno <guilabel>Paleta</guilabel> prikazuje barve nitke, ki so trenutno v tej "
"paleti vzorcev, kot barvne bloke in po želji s simboli, ki so povezani z "
"vsako barvo. Če kazalec miške premaknete nad barvni blok, se prikaže namig "
"orodja, ki prikazuje številko barve in ime te barve. S klikom na barvo "
"izberete to barvo za naslednjo funkcijo slikanja ali risanja."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using your &RMB; on the <guilabel>Palette</guilabel> view will activate a "
"context menu allowing you to perform several functions on the palette. See "
"<link linkend=\"commands\">the command reference</link> for more details on "
"their use."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo &RMB; v pogledu <guilabel>Paleta</guilabel> aktivira kontekstni "
"meni, ki vam omogoča izvajanje več funkcij na paleti. Glejte <link linkend="
"\"commands\">referenco ukazov</link> za več podrobnosti o njihovi uporabi."
